title: Poker Challenge 4.3.2
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

This enjoyable, easy-to-learn card game cleverly blends the
rules of poker with solitaire. The object of the game is to
identify poker hands within a deck of cards that has been dealt
and evenly spread out face up. Once a hand has been marked to
play, the cards that make up the hand are removed, points are
awarded, and any cards above them fall down to take their place.
(The game&#039;s screen shot shows an example of the concept).

Version 4.3.2 enhances the Player Selection Screen so that
novice players are given instructions about how to select a
player and begin a new game.
